OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1776963955
OL,3,CBoy, 16, jailed for raping teenage
OL,4,Cgirl in Worcester
OL,6,FHe was sentenced to a further two and
OL,7,Fa half years for the sexual assault,
OL,8,Fwhich will run concurrently with the
OL,9,Fsentence for rape. He will also be
OL,10,Fplaced on the Sex Offenders' Register
OL,11,Ffor life.
OL,13,FHe was 15 when he raped a 17-year-old
OL,14,Fgirl in Cripplegate Park in Worcester
OL,15,Fat around 2am on Sunday 10 August 2025.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1776963955
OL,3,CBoy, 16, jailed for raping teenage
OL,4,Cgirl in Worcester
OL,6,FWest Mercia Police found him through
OL,7,FCCTV footage, which showed him
OL,8,Ffollowing the victim over Worcester
OL,9,Fbridge and into the park. He was
OL,10,Farrested within hours of the incident
OL,11,Fand charged two days later.
OL,13,FDetective Inspector Sharon Wallace-
OL,14,FRathmell, who led the investigation,
OL,15,Fsaid: "This was an incredibly
OL,16,Ftraumatic experience for the victim,
OL,17,Fand one which also shocked the local
OL,18,Fcommunity.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
