OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1776963955
OL,3,CBoy, 16, jailed for raping teenage
OL,4,Cgirl in Worcester
OL,6,F"I'm pleased that the boy, who cannot
OL,7,Fbe named for legal reasons due to his
OL,8,Fage, will be detained for a
OL,9,Fsignificant period of time and won't
OL,10,Fbe able to cause further harm.
OL,12,F"We take all reports of rape and
OL,13,Fsexual assault incredibly seriously,
OL,14,Fand I'd like to commend the victim for
OL,15,Fhaving the courage to report the
OL,16,Fincident to us so quickly.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
